  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/665e6792e079605f2415118a927f1928.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/665e6792e079605f2415118a927f1928.webm?t=1765032743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Isle of Lye is a specially constructed testing ground for the Gordian Society, and as fate would have it, you have ended up here.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you to rise to the challenge and find a way out of this place, all the while competing to become a full fledged member of this enigmatic organisation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/1b74ab3f65d8c74416f0f9d22f025f33.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/1b74ab3f65d8c74416f0f9d22f025f33.webm?t=1765032743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the island, you will get to know the quirky Lye family and their numerous associates. From servants to family members, everyone is more than they let on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find the black sheep of the family or the traitor in the mansion? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or perhaps you'd prefer to search for someone else's carefully hidden treasures...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you get to the bottom of every mystery?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/b43a424610d1a6d091be1fb32d06e56d.webp?t=1765032743\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/b43a424610d1a6d091be1fb32d06e56d.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=202 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/665e6792e079605f2415118a927f1928.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/665e6792e079605f2415118a927f1928.webm?t=1765032743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Isle of Lye is a specially constructed testing ground for the Gordian Society, and as fate would have it, you have ended up here.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you to rise to the challenge and find a way out of this place, all the while competing to become a full fledged member of this enigmatic organisation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/1b74ab3f65d8c74416f0f9d22f025f33.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/1b74ab3f65d8c74416f0f9d22f025f33.webm?t=1765032743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the island, you will get to know the quirky Lye family and their numerous associates. From servants to family members, everyone is more than they let on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find the black sheep of the family or the traitor in the mansion? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or perhaps you'd prefer to search for someone else's carefully hidden treasures...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you get to the bottom of every mystery?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/b43a424610d1a6d091be1fb32d06e56d.webp?t=1765032743\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528220/extras/b43a424610d1a6d091be1fb32d06e56d.poster.avif?t=1765032743\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=202 /></picture></span></p>",
